name: Cane Code
short_description:
Cane Code is small program language, but on them you can write you OS! I do not want to advertise their products and so on, I just came to show you Cane Code!
- "Wow, what a thing! It's fun," you do not think. And now more about Cane Code. I just explain what it is (and what it eats).
Cane Code - is an esoteric programming language like Brainf *ck, but it contains only digits, only the hardcore. And once they: 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 (and two trinkets, ie they are not required, but can be used in some versions - is 9 and 0).
